# tfe_team_organization_members

Add or remove one or more team members using a [tfe_organization_membership](organization_membership.html).

~> **NOTE** on managing team memberships: Terraform currently provides four resources for managing team memberships. This - along with [tfe_team_organization_member](team_organization_member.html) - is the preferred method as it allows you to add members to a team by email addresses. The [tfe_team_organization_member](team_organization_member.html) is used to manage a single team membership whereas [tfe_team_organization_members](team_organization_members.html) is used to manage all team memberships at once. All four resources cannot be used for the same team simultaneously.

~> **NOTE:** This resource requires using the provider with HCP Terraform or an instance of Terraform Enterprise at least as recent as v202004-1.

